---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="尤克里里练习台" desc="尤克里里和弦图、拨弦音色合成与换和弦节拍训练，全部在本地运行">
<main class="wrap reader">
  <a class="back mono" href="/music/">← 音乐</a>
  <h1 class="rd-title">尤克里里练习台</h1>
  <div class="meta mono">
    <span class="sw" style="background:var(--c-life);"></span>
    <span>高音 G 定弦 GCEA · 和弦图 · 拨弦合成 · 换和弦训练</span>
  </div>

  <p style="max-width:820px; color:var(--ink2); font-size:14.5px;">
    音色用 Karplus-Strong 算法实时合成 —— 一段白噪声在延迟线里反复低通反馈，就长出拨弦的泛音与衰减，
    不用任何采样、零外链。点和弦听声、看指法，再用下面的节拍训练器练「一分钟换和弦」。
  </p>

  <h2 class="uke-h mono">和弦库<span>　点一下：听声 · 看大图 · 加入训练序列</span></h2>
  <div id="uke-lib" class="uke-lib"></div>
  <div id="uke-now" class="uke-now"></div>

  <h2 class="uke-h mono">换和弦训练<span>　在节拍内切换和弦，先跟示范再自己弹</span></h2>
  <div class="uke-presets mono">
    <span style="color:var(--ink2);">常用套路：</span>
    <button type="button" class="uke-preset pie-btn" data-set="C,Am,F,G">C–Am–F–G</button>
    <button type="button" class="uke-preset pie-btn" data-set="C,G,Am,F">C–G–Am–F</button>
    <button type="button" class="uke-preset pie-btn" data-set="C,F">C ⇄ F</button>
    <button type="button" class="uke-preset pie-btn" data-set="G,D,Em,C">G–D–Em–C</button>
    <button type="button" class="uke-preset pie-btn" data-set="Am,Dm,G7,C">Am–Dm–G7–C</button>
  </div>
  <div id="uke-selected" class="uke-selected"></div>

  <div class="shu-panel">
    <label>速度
      <input id="uke-bpm" type="range" min="40" max="160" value="60" style="width:150px;" />
      <b class="mono" style="color:var(--ink);"><span id="uke-bpmv">60</span> BPM</b>
    </label>
    <label>每和弦
      <select id="uke-bpc" class="mono">
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="4" selected>4</option>
        <option value="6">6</option>
        <option value="8">8</option>
      </select> 拍
    </label>
    <label class="mono"><input type="checkbox" id="uke-demo" checked /> 示范扫弦</label>
    <button type="button" class="pie-btn primary" id="uke-start">▶ 开始训练</button>
    <button type="button" class="pie-btn" id="uke-clear">清空</button>
    <p class="mono hint2" id="uke-hint"></p>
  </div>

  <div id="uke-stage" class="uke-stage">
    <div class="uke-count mono" id="uke-count"></div>
    <div class="uke-stagemain">
      <div id="uke-nowbig" class="uke-bigwrap"></div>
      <div class="uke-stagetext">
        <b id="uke-nowname">—</b>
        <span class="mono" id="uke-nextname">下一个　—</span>
        <div class="uke-beats" id="uke-beats"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mono" style="max-width:820px; color:var(--ink2); font-size:11.5px; margin-top:26px;">
    指法取常见把位，同一和弦各有多种按法；声音与节拍全部在本地实时合成，不加载任何音频文件。
  </p>
</main>
</Base>

<script>
  import '../../scripts/music/ukulele.js';
</script>
